{"tid":1857683,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"做緊黃色經濟圈定黃色義工圈？","createTime":"2020-02-02T09:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T14:31:10.000Z","uid":88169,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"493a768a2b3ae76d37329041b7ea82f2da40bc87","tid":1857683,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"人地黃店入到貨賣口罩又話人地人血。<br />\n<br />\n個個話支持經濟圈又唔撚比人賺少少。<br />\n<br />\n成百萬口罩貨又唔比人賺錢。<br />\n<br />\n訂貨入貨人手，壓住成百萬，又要驚比大陸狗偷，又驚比人放飛機，又驚比人呃，為乜柒？<br />\n<br />\n可以賺10倍錢既而家賺你幾蚊就屌。<br />\n<br />\n而家供不應求，demand supply都識啦，缺撚到咁加個5蚊屌到人化，仲邊有人肯幫你呀香港人。<br />\n<br />\n再加上個撚個天才以為批發就一撚定唔加價既，來貨價貴就要人做翻原價。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家同路人可以撐下？查一查其實真係知道真黃定假黃。下下屌人人血真係點樣會有人幫你呀？ </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈唔好逼人捐又咩啦，好多小店/有心人有source有少少錢想幫手，但係真係afford唔到蝕架。。。"},{"pid":"01005ff9708ce78726141cb729316c56d0511867","tid":1857683,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:59:25.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"77794420cb6d32c1903b69864ee6869e57dcf696","tid":1857683,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"8153742bf00baa8a8451821c098462747c6f80fe","tid":1857683,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:59:49.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"8a06ac38539b6efb8bc31fcf409fc541847976fc","tid":1857683,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:00:00.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"77008d12027c22c757a359b8105ffd91d097b727","tid":1857683,"uid":88169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:00:12.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"fbb0626f8536e0f5eaca862071229ac47166a59d","tid":1857683,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:02:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家幫手推一推，正個評</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"fo